data.description: WHY WAIT TO BUILD? Newly built Move-in-Ready 2018 3-bedroom home in the highly sought-after Community of Carlton Lakes  located in Riverview, Florida. This 3 bedroom 2 bath 2 Car Garage is 1509 sqft FENCED BACKYARD. As you enter the foyer, you will find your beautiful open floor plan. This home comes with a spacious gourmet kitchen, your new home includes granite kitchen countertops, luxury wood style vinyl floor, and stainless steel appliances, along with energy-efficient insulation, Low-E windows, and a kitchen island that overlooks the family room and dining room, perfect for entertaining family and friends. In the rest of the home, you will find the owner's suite, the owner's full bath shower & a large walk-in closet.The other 2 bedrooms are separated and a second full bathroom with tub provides great privacy. There is a nice amount of yard space around this home giving you more space for outdoor activities. This is a great location to call home! Within the community, enjoy amenities including a fitness center, community pool, recreational facilities, and other common areas. The HOA is so you can save money and enjoy a low-maintenance-free lifestyle! You will be close to the newly built Goodrich Riverview 14 GDX movie theater & you can enjoy living near the best of Tampa Bay with beaches, entertainment, and outdoor attractions nearby! Major roadways such as US-301, I-75, and US-41 provide travel routes throughout the Tampa area, MacDill, Airports, and easy access to Orlando or Miami. And, you will love the convenience of shops and several new restaurants just minutes from your front door.*Property qualifies for 100% financing, HOMETOWN HEROES FIRST LOAN PROGRAM Hillsborough county is offering up to $35,000 towards closing costs or a down payment!
